     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       n wnng nthng
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Whl mnmlsm strvs t wn lttl — nt mch mr thn y nd — wht f w fllwd ths t n xtrm, jst fr fn.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wht f w wnd nthng t ll?
      </p>
      <p>
       I dn’t mn w hv n clthng r shltr r tls, bt rthr tht w bndn th d f prvt prprty. It’s  rdcl d (thgh nt  nw n), bt smthng t thnk bt.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wht f w hd thngs w sd, bt ddn’t wn? Wht f w sd clthng whn w ndd t, bt thn whn w ddn’t w gv t t  plc tht hlds thm (myb  clthng lbrry). And th sm wld pply t ny pssssns, frm cmptrs t tls t tlvsns t dshs nd s n.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wht bt hsng nd crs? Cr shrng s lrdy bng dn n sm plcs, nd th sm cld b dn wth bcycls — bk lbrrs ll vr th plc. Mss trnst, f crs, s nthr shrd sltn.
      </p>
      <p>
       Shrd hms r ls nthng nw, thgh t’s  prtty frgn d fr mst f s wh r sd t th prvcy f r wn hms. Thr r mny pssblts n ths fld, hwvr, ncldng bt nt lmtd t:
      </p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        Hsng lbrrs, whr smll nd mdm nts cld b gvn t ppl s ndd, nd thn rtrnd t th pl whn ppl mv.
       </li>
       <li>
        Hsng c-ps, whr ppl shr lrg hms nd th rspnsblts f mngng nd mntnng thm.
       </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
       Whn y bndn th d f prvt wnrshp,  lt f pssblts rs — lmtd nly by r mgntns.
       <br/>
       <span id="more-452">
       </span>
       <br/>
       Bt why vn cnsdr ths rdcl chng? A fw rsns:
      </p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        I lk th d f lvng vry lght — sng nly wht y nd, gvng bck t th cmmnty wht y dn’t, nd nvr bng brdnd by wnrshp f mtrl thngs.
       </li>
       <li>
        Ownrshp s t xsts s wstfl — ftn w hld n t thngs w dn’t s, tht thr ppl cld s, bcs w bght thm nd wn thm. Bt f w nly kpt thngs tht w s, nd rtrnd thm whn nt n s, wth th d tht w cld lwys gt thm whn w ndd thm, thr wld b lss wst. Lss thrwng thngs n lndflls s wll.
       </li>
       <li>
        Ppl wh nd thngs — lk clthng nd shltr — wld nt b dnd thm.
       </li>
       <li>
        Thr wld b  lt lss ccmltn f wlth nt th hnds f  fw, whch sms t m t b  rlly bd scl d. Ths crts xtrm pvrty, crm, nd nhppnss. In plcs whr ncm nqlty s rltvly lw, thr s  grtr dgr f hppnss nd lwr crm lvls. (
        <a href="http://theminimalist.net/2009/05/14/income-distribution-vs-happiness/">
         Rd ths
        </a>
        , fr xmpl.)
       </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
       Anywy. Ths s bvsly nt gng t hppn vrnght, nr d I thnk t shld. Agn, jst smthng t cnsdr.
      </p>
      <p>
       I knw ppl wll pnt t fld xprmnts sch s th
       <span class="caps">
        USSR
       </span>
       whr th bndnmnt f prvt prprty ddn’t wrk vn  lttl. I gr wth tht ssssmnt, bt th prblm ws tht t ws ll stt-cntrlld. I thnk llwng th gvrnmnt t cntrl prprty s  vry bd d. Ppl shld cntrl prprty — w cld st p vlntry, dmcrtc ssctns t mntn bk nd cr nd bk nd clthng lbrrs nd hsng nd ll tht.
      </p>
      <p>
       In fct, t wld tk n chng n gvrnmnt t strt sch ssctns tdy — w cld jst gt tgthr (vn n th Intrnt) nd vlntrly strt thm, try thm t, xprmnt, s f t wrks. All t wld tk s  grp f ppl wh wnt t try th cncpt t, wh rspct ch thr ngh t nt try t cnsldt pwr t  fw ppl. In fct, prtctns gnst th cnsldtn f pwr shld b pt n plc, s tht vryn hs n ql sy n ll sss tht ffct thm — w cn’t hv rprsnttvs wh mk dcsns fr s.
      </p>
      <p>
       Agn, nt nw ds. Ths g bck t th 1800s nd n fct ths s hw trdtnl scts fnctnd, fr th mst prt, ntl kngs nd prsts nd lrds nd mrchnts strtd tkng wnrshp f thngs.
      </p>
      <p>
       Chng s pssbl, f w kp r mnds pn nd llw rslvs t xplr th pssblts.
      </p>
      <p>
       <small>
       </small>
      </p>
